{"tid":2270924,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲橋本環奈身形漸趨大媽化　節目中驚現巨臀搶晒Fo","createTime":"2020-11-04T09:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T08:00:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":19,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"5cacdbd284c2966037564bf803543aedcbfb8912","tid":2270924,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"被喻為「千年一遇美少女」，現年21歲的日本女星橋本環奈，雖然擁有迷人漂亮的甜美靚樣，可是她近年的體型卻開始橫向發展，愈來愈肥。她曾自爆愛上飲酒和打牌，並在節目上驚現啤酒肚及雙下巴，甚至被指頸以上很讚，頸以下則令人慘不忍睹。<br />\n<br />\n橋本環奈最近成為NTV電視台節目《I Love大家的動物園》的固定班底，在當地播出的最新一集入面，她就照顧初生老虎仔，並與老虎仔一起玩，可是卻在鏡頭前展現出巨臀，圓潤的身型十分搶鏡，年紀輕輕已趨向大媽化。"},{"pid":"88bfc6d70fcdc99b617184326b375fb068824e75","tid":2270924,"uid":16659,"like":162,"dislike":13,"score":149,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201104/400629089922191360297436.jpeg/0Aot1QM1Hfgy3QGYv4SrP2Vo4KsJRMaLx_QuLMf0Liw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201104%2F400629089922191360297436.jpeg%2F0Aot1QM1Hfgy3QGYv4SrP2Vo4KsJRMaLx_QuLMf0Liw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c142a4d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fb0206eae5dc691f0d6d62f896ab8a9e0e3ec3a","tid":2270924,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"嘩痴咗孖筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a883eb7af61035ed08e91bb1068e98cfde50b6","tid":2270924,"uid":261849,"like":16,"dislike":31,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"無樣又矮又肥.....引退啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ab4bb247f3c0de69a0fba1c2045f6cd3be6cc1","tid":2270924,"uid":16659,"like":111,"dislike":9,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img