44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/8zx6394454x51.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2F8zx6394454x51.gif&h=22be04cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"最後粒炸彈點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e835056cbe0203a8825b16bcde80e329b859fba","tid":2270924,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"點解佢啲牙邊咁黑 <br />\n係咪遮都遮唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7605e53dde3e369ea59332f66059cbaabb2caa31","tid":2270924,"uid":235174,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f81fd16ddea626cbf25e88b51352460e2f40c235","tid":2270924,"uid":370148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13ca3d22ebc659691f379937674a1d29e71cb001","tid":2270924,"uid":235174,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/8zx6394454x51.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2F8zx6394454x51.gif&h=22be04cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"最後粒炸彈點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T12:05:35.000Z","msg":"This gif is real and things like this happened occasionally in WWII. The plane is a F6F Hellcat. The rocket looks to be an HVAR commonly called a holy moses rocket. Lots of planes trying to carrier land would miss the hook and either hit the bridge or if they were damaged would make a hard belly landing. If they did catch the hook the force of them getting on the hook or landing harshly would &quot;launch&quot; the rocket off the hard point on the wing and send it over the ship like above or it would hit the ship and cause damage. This video, <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qup7wpLYglU&amp;t=1s&amp;ab_channel=UnknownWW2InColor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dqup7wpLYglU%26t%3D1s%26ab_channel%3DUnknownWW2InColor&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3Vcys3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=e324f64d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qup7wpLYglU&amp;t=1s&amp;ab_channel=UnknownWW2InColor</a> , shows almost the exact scenario unfolding in color as well as other carrier mishaps that commonly happened during WWII.<br />\n<br />\nOr Tenet<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qLbQxwp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqLbQxwp.gif&h=cc6e4560&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96f82c39aa5e261427de7a8f657709ec967ebf44","tid":2270924,"uid":199592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bf860e97121ddb96b762840e7f976712d01cebf","tid":2270924,"uid":172144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:55:52.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得日本細路女就出道個D唔少都比人谷身材谷肥晒<br />\n菅谷梨沙子又係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"肥都被迫，瘦又話人被迫減肥減到無波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}